# Coinbase Smart Wallet popup requires `same-origin-allow-popups`, NOT `same-origin`.
# Setting just `same-origin` silently breaks the keys.coinbase.com popup.
# Research source: Base docs § "Popup Tips", May 2026.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin-allow-popups
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=(self)
